content: App is fine. BUT. Be very careful. I would not trust this company. They do not let you delete your account. I repeat, they do not let you delete your account or your data. Very suspicious! I followed their instructions and raised 4 support tickets via the app to DELETE my account. Each time, Grab automatically change my ticket to an "Account Deactivation Request". Then, the agent would say they have deactivated my account and immediately close the ticket. But my account is still active! Lies!

I accidentally deleted my review when I was to abt to edit it as a reply to the developers response. I don't see any pending amount whatsoever on my payment method! Even in my transaction history on the app. I removed my CC details as soon as the payment for my ride was done. Shame on you people who put hold on a certain amount w/o notice which I have not seen since the time I used the app! If only I could change my rating to negative, I'd be at peace.
A little more expensive than a taxi but it is worth every penny. You are paying for the ease, comfort, security and cleanliness.

content: Frustrated! This app was 1 star in Ninh Binh which is rural but a major tourist destination 2 hrs south of Hanoi.
